func newEnv(n int64) *Env {
	e := new(Env)
	e.M = 0
	e.N = n
	e.T = make([]bool, n)
	e.S = make([]bool, n)
	e.Slack = make([]int64, n)
	e.Slackx = make([]int64, n)
	e.Prev = make([]int64, n)
	e.Xy = make([]int64, n)
	e.Yx = make([]int64, n)
	e.Lx = make([]int64, n)
	e.Ly = make([]int64, n)
	var i int64
	for i = 0; i < n; i++ {
		e.Xy[i] = -1
		e.Yx[i] = -1
	}
	return e
}
